original_text:
The MISSION of the RNC is to encourage community participation in City Governance.
To provide an inclusive and open forum for public discussion of issues of interest to the RNC, including City governance, the needs of the RNC, the delivery of City services to the RNC area, and other matters of a City wide nature;
To advise the City on issues of interest to the RNC, including City governance, the needs of the RNC, the delivery of City services to the RNC area, and other matters of a City wide nature;
To initiate, execute and support projects for the physical, social and cultural improvement of the RNC area; and
To facilitate communication between the City and Stakeholders on issues of concern to the community and/or the Stakeholders.

